<br>
------------------ EQ Forums ------------------<br>
General Discussion -- all non-specific EQ chat<br>
Apprentices' Hall -- For Q&amp;A discussion of all questions related to spells, hunting grounds, xp plaves, quests, and anything similar.<br>
Sorcerers' Tower -- For Q&amp;A End Game discussion for raid behavior, dps on various high level spells. Loosely can be considered to be anything dealing with wizards level 60 or higher.<br>
PvP Discussion and Tactics -- self explanatory<br>
Class Bugs -- bugs only, should be modded very harshly, should be used so we can keep track of bugs with quests, zones, spells, whatever.<br>
Tales of Norrath -- Roleplay forum.<br>
------------------ OT Forums ------------------<br>
Off Topic Forum -- self explanatory<br>
Polls Forum -- self explanatory<br>
Rant Forum -- self explanatory <br>
<br>
I removed class balance since almost everyone posts their class balance stuff in general anyway. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ikeya>Ikeya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<br>Stamping Out Stupidity</span><br>  Posts: 3394<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/7/03 3:37:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26402.topic&index=46>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> I suggest renaming the OT forum to the Political Forum. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
